      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for a daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and several small door dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it will likely require new tires and a standard tune-up in the near future. It is a well-used vehicle that is priced to reflect its current state and maintenance needs.",
