    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable, stylish ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I'm selling my car, and it has been absolutely wonderful to own. It's in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and I've made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty handles it all with ease. It\u2019s got plenty of heart and is just waiting for a new owner to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 31500.0,
